## Active Referrers
| Referrer | Referrals Sent | Signups | Videos Uploaded | Tier |
|----------|---------------|---------|-----------------|------|

## Referral Chains
- {Founder A} â†’ {Founder B} â†’ {Founder C} (3-level chain!)

## Top Referrers (This Month)
1. {name} â€” {N} successful referrals
2. {name} â€” {N} successful referrals

## Program Metrics
- Total referral links generated: {N}
- Click-through rate: {%}
- Signup rate from referral: {%}
- Video upload rate from referral: {%}
- Average referral chain depth: {N}
```

## Viral Loop Design

```
Founder uploads video
    â†’ Gets investor views
    â†’ Gets excited, shares with founder friends
    â†’ Friends upload videos
    â†’ More videos attract more investors
    â†’ More investors attract more founders
    â†’ Repeat
```

## Referral Content Templates

### Social Share (For Founders to Post)
```
Just uploaded my 90-sec pitch to @PitchTok and already
got {X} investor views. Way better than cold emailing
pitch decks. If you're raising, check it out:
{referral_link}
```

### Email Forward Template
```
Hey â€” thought you'd be interested in this. I uploaded
a short pitch video and investors are actually watching.
Way easier than cold outreach. Here's my link:
{referral_link}
```

## Identifying Potential Referrers
Look for founders who:
- Reply positively to outreach
- Upload a video within 24 hours
- Have large social following (can amplify)
- Are in active founder communities
- Have previously referred other products

Flag these in lead records with `referral_potential: high`
